3, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I read Bhagwat Gita and always tried to do what I am supposed to do, leaving everything else to god.\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1254, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bhagavad_Gita\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bhagwat Gita\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bhagavad_Gita\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bhagavad_Gita\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We can not fight destiny.\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u009dBhaker\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122s shooting story began in early 2016 when she took up the sport on her father Ramkishen Bhaker\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122s insistence at Universal Senior Secondary School in Goria, Jhajjar.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1457, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1449, \"end\": 1456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IIT_Delhi\", \"score\": 0.8682940825088106, \"rank\": 0.15168351205297187, \"text\": \"Jhajjar\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IIT_Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IIT_Delhi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In just one year, the Class XI girl became the national champion in all three categories \\u00e2\\u20ac\\\" youth, junior and women \\u00e2\\u20ac\\\" of the 10m air pistol event.\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1607, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just eight years after taking up the sport, the 2020 Arjuna awardee has an Olympics bronze.CM Hails Bhaker for Winning BronzeHaryana Chief Minister Nayab Singh Saini on Sunday extended his heartfelt congratulations to Manu Bhaker for her outstanding achievement in securing a bronze medal in the 10-meter air pistol event at the Paris Olympics-2024.\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1957, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1661, \"end\": 1667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arjuna_Award\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2386682464420925e-20, \"text\": \"Arjuna\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"