ardee has an Olympics bronze.\", \"from\": 4693, \"to\": 4784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4746, \"end\": 4752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arjuna_Award\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2386682464420925e-20, \"text\": \"Arjuna\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arjuna_Award\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arjuna_Award\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"CM Hails Bhaker for Winning Bronze  Haryana Chief Minister Nayab Singh Saini on Sunday extended his heartfelt congratulations to Manu Bhaker for her outstanding achievement in securing a bronze medal in the 10-meter air pistol event at the Paris Olympics-2024.\", \"from\": 4788, \"to\": 5048, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4824, \"end\": 4831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3900831681423928e-14, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}, {\"begin\": 4847, \"end\": 4858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nayab_Singh\", \"score\": 0.9999999971319085, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nayab Singh\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nayab_Singh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nayab_Singh\"}, {\"begin\": 4859, \"end\": 4864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saini\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Saini\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saini\"}, {\"begin\": 4917, \"end\": 4928, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manu_Bhaker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Manu Bhaker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manu_Bhaker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manu_Bhaker\"}, {\"begin\": 5028, \"end\": 5042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Saini, in his message, lauded Bhaker for her remarkable performance and historical achievement, which has brought immense pride to both Haryana and the entire nation.\", \"from\": 5049, \"to\": 5215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5049, \"end\": 5054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saini\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Saini\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saini\"}, {\"begin\": 5185, \"end\": 5192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3900831681423928e-14, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Praising her dedication, hard work, and perseverance that led to this prestigious accomplishment on the global stage, Saini said: \\u00e2\\u20ac\\u0153Bhaker\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122s success is a testament to her extraordinary talent and relentless effort.\", \"from\": 5219, \"to\": 5436, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5337, \"end\": 5342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saini\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Saini\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has not only made Haryana proud but also set an inspiring example for aspiring athletes across the country\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u00a6We are confident that our players will continue to excel and bring more laurels to the state and the country.\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u009d    Also congratulating all the athletes from Haryana participating in the ongoing Paris Olympics, the Chief Minister expressed his optimism that these athletes will continue to perform exceptionally well and secure more medals for India.\", \"from\": 5437, \"to\": 5900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5459, \"end\": 5466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3900831681423928e-14, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}, {\"begin\": 5708, \"end\": 5715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3900831681423928e-14, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}, {\"begin\": 5894, \"end\": 5899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9987294755015594, \"rank\": 0.0010973706739602165, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u0153Our government has implemented numerous initiatives and policies to support and nurture the sporting talent in Haryana.\", \"from\": 5901, \"to\": 6023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6015, \"end\": 6022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3900831681423928e-14, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are dedicated to providing our athletes with the best facilities, training, and support to help them achieve their full potential,\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u009d he added.\", \"from\": 6024, \"to\": 6170, \"entities\": []}]}"